OL,5, Sainsbury's has announced pay rises    
OL,6, from March as supermarkets continue    
OL,7, their battle to retain workers.        
OL,9,FIt will increase minimum pay for       
OL,10,Femployees outside London to #12 an     
OL,11,Fhour, with wages for staff in the      
OL,12,Fcapital increasing to #13.15 an hour.  
OL,14,FThe increase means all of its workers  
OL,15,Fwill be paid the voluntary Real Living 
OL,16,FWage, which is higher than the         
OL,17,Fcompulsory National Living Wage.       
